description: A region located in the suburbs of Sevilla that belonged to the kingdom of Alfonso X. It is now known as El Aljarafe.

locations.details: Polygonal geometry representing the perimeter of the modern administrative area of El Aljarafe, which is associated with the medieval site of Axaraf de Seuilla. Geometry derived from an OpenStreetMap relation.
